1
00:00:24,930 --> 00:00:26,810
♪Wine banners flutter, carriages pass by♪

2
00:00:26,810 --> 00:00:29,610
♪The streets ablaze with revelry♪

3
00:00:32,440 --> 00:00:34,240
♪His name in gold, proud blooms adorn♪

4
00:00:34,240 --> 00:00:37,260
♪Who lingers now♪

5
00:00:39,080 --> 00:00:40,320
♪Seek one true peace♪

6
00:00:40,320 --> 00:00:42,250
♪Yet fate hangs on a thread so fine♪

7
00:00:42,680 --> 00:00:43,970
♪Longing has taken root♪

8
00:00:43,970 --> 00:00:46,140
♪Like flowers yet not♪

9
00:00:46,700 --> 00:00:48,120
♪Words fall too short♪

10
00:00:48,120 --> 00:00:50,040
♪So I ride far♪

11
00:00:50,040 --> 00:00:52,780
♪To chase the dream beyond the skyline♪

12
00:00:53,040 --> 00:00:54,200
♪No regret♪

13
00:00:54,200 --> 00:00:55,790
♪Through the flow of years♪

14
00:00:55,790 --> 00:00:57,580
♪Over waves and cliffs♪

15
00:00:57,580 --> 00:00:58,830
♪Where worries end♪

16
00:00:58,830 --> 00:01:01,360
♪May winds bear word of who recalls♪

17
00:01:01,360 --> 00:01:02,940
♪But fate cries loud♪

18
00:01:02,940 --> 00:01:04,920
♪Envying a world too pure to keep♪

19
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:07,580
♪Seasons bloom, yet lips grow weak♪

20
00:01:07,930 --> 00:01:09,850
♪Through dust of time, all mortals stray♪

21
00:01:09,850 --> 00:01:11,600
♪As seasons weave their gold and grey♪

22
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:13,560
♪I roam the earth and heavens freely♪

23
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:15,390
♪Why ask the road back home to be♪

24
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:18,010
♪Sun and moon part, stars remain silent♪

25
00:01:18,010 --> 00:01:22,510
♪Through endless night, dawn paints its art♪

26
00:01:24,460 --> 00:01:29,980
=Serendipity=

27
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,940
=Episode 17=

28
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,000
Sister.

29
00:01:38,230 --> 00:01:39,840
It's really you, Sister.

30
00:01:42,870 --> 00:01:44,120
You're alive.

31
00:01:48,230 --> 00:01:49,120
Where have you been

32
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,400
this past year?

33
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:51,880
I've searched everywhere for you.

34
00:01:52,590 --> 00:01:53,870
After we parted,

35
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:56,510
I sneaked into the capital.

36
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,040
Later, I was rescued

37
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,920
by a family named Zhang.

38
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:02,120
I took the jade pendant

39
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,740
to the Imperial Music Office
to find you,

40
00:02:04,230 --> 00:02:06,200
but the steward told me

41
00:02:06,870 --> 00:02:08,630
you were already in the Lu Residence.

42
00:02:09,710 --> 00:02:10,550
Then came

43
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:14,470
that incident
at the Hereditary Privilege Banquet.

44
00:02:15,590 --> 00:02:17,280
Speak! Why was Zhang Song's jade pendant

45
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:18,590
in Lu Wencai's possession

46
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:20,310
to threaten Lady Yuanying?

47
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,360
My master

48
00:02:21,500 --> 00:02:22,720
took a liking to Lady Yuanying,

49
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,430
but she refused him outright.

50
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,680
This Liu Yuanying...

51
00:02:28,500 --> 00:02:29,990
I offered her so much gold and jewels,

52
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,800
yet she remained stubborn.

53
00:02:33,030 --> 00:02:34,910
She rejects courtesy
and invites punishment.

54
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,000
If bribery fails,

55
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:39,240
threats must suffice.

56
00:02:40,700 --> 00:02:42,160
Earlier at the Imperial Music Office,

57
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,520
I overheard the steward mention

58
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,680
she had a younger brother

59
00:02:45,700 --> 00:02:46,940
searching for her with a jade pendant.

60
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,710
Her brother?

61
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,710
He's the son of a disgraced official.

62
00:02:52,870 --> 00:02:55,310
He must be in hiding.

63
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,630
This identity could be exploited.

64
00:02:58,870 --> 00:03:00,470
For that beast Lu Wencai,

65
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:02,030
you'd ruin your future?

66
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,400
Wenyuan,

67
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,240
is it worth it?

68
00:03:10,430 --> 00:03:11,840
He violated you.

69
00:03:12,310 --> 00:03:14,030
If I don't kill him,

70
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,960
I swear I'll cease to be human.

71
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:20,310
I infiltrated the academy

72
00:03:20,630 --> 00:03:22,630
solely to avenge you.

73
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,080
Sister,

74
00:03:28,030 --> 00:03:29,030
don't cry.

75
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:31,150
Our reunion

76
00:03:31,710 --> 00:03:33,910
should be joyous.

77
00:03:33,910 --> 00:03:35,430
You're my only family left

78
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,870
in this world.

79
00:03:38,030 --> 00:03:38,910
The sole reason

80
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:40,520
I keep living is you.

81
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,680
How could you bear to leave me alone?

82
00:03:49,910 --> 00:03:50,750
Wenyuan...

83
00:03:52,710 --> 00:03:53,550
Wenyuan...

84
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:55,270
Wenyuan!

85
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,640
Wenyuan!

86
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:01,430
Wenyuan!

87
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,400
Sister,

88
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,710
had I known this,

89
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:06,280
I wouldn't have sought you out.

90
00:04:06,710 --> 00:04:07,550
Then

91
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:09,520
he wouldn't have

92
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:10,800
deceived you.

93
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:11,640
Wenyuan,

94
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:12,910
it's not your fault.

95
00:04:12,910 --> 00:04:13,750
Not your fault.

96
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:16,510
You're my only kin now.

97
00:04:16,510 --> 00:04:17,560
If you die,

98
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,190
I won't live either.

99
00:04:19,310 --> 00:04:20,150
Sister,

100
00:04:21,070 --> 00:04:21,910
promise me.

101
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:23,920
Don't cry.

102
00:04:24,630 --> 00:04:25,680
Alright?

103
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,270
No more tears.

104
00:04:46,070 --> 00:04:46,910
Wenyuan!

105
00:04:48,170 --> 00:04:49,040
Wenyuan,

106
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:50,680
wake up. Look at me.

107
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,560
Wenyuan,

108
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:53,510
wake up and look at me.

109
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,800
Wenyuan, look at me one last time!

110
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:58,070
Wenyuan, open your eyes!

111
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:01,920
Wenyuan!

112
00:05:04,270 --> 00:05:05,120
Wenyuan...

113
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:12,790
Soon...

114
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,000
I'll...

115
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:17,190
I'll join you soon.

116
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,430
Let me die!

117
00:05:19,430 --> 00:05:20,510
What are you doing?

118
00:05:20,510 --> 00:05:21,830
With Father and Wenyuan gone,

119
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:23,120
what meaning does my life hold?

120
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,020
Yuanying!

121
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:25,690
Your father was forced
to frame his friend

122
00:05:25,690 --> 00:05:27,070
due to others' schemes.

123
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,270
He likely died filled with regret

124
00:05:29,870 --> 00:05:31,310
for leaving your family in turmoil.

125
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:33,920
We must

126
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,430
uncover the full truth.

127
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:55,480
The reunion brings parting.

128
00:05:56,630 --> 00:05:58,160
Though not blood siblings,

129
00:05:59,390 --> 00:06:00,720
their genuine bond

130
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,920
moves hearts.

131
00:06:16,180 --> 00:06:20,020
(Mingli Hall)

132
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,000
Tang...

133
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,510
Lady Su.

134
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:33,120
We're both from Jianglin.

135
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,070
Just call me Tangli henceforth.

136
00:06:36,270 --> 00:06:37,110
However,

137
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,310
we weren't

138
00:06:39,310 --> 00:06:40,800
particularly close before.

139
00:06:41,510 --> 00:06:42,680
Why do you

140
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,120
seek me now?

141
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,950
Certain matters perplex me.

142
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,950
I come seeking answers.

143
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,720
What could I, a criminal slave,

144
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:02,750
help with?

145
00:07:07,430 --> 00:07:08,390
Missed.

146
00:07:12,390 --> 00:07:13,630
According to Zhang Song,

147
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,430
he committed two crimes.

148
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,480
The hidden arrow in Huantao Study

149
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:19,630
and the plaque in Mingli Hall.

150
00:07:20,310 --> 00:07:22,680
He claims he accidentally
found the arrow

151
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,430
and overheard

152
00:07:24,430 --> 00:07:25,950
about the plaque's damage.

153
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:27,870
How coincidental.

154
00:07:27,870 --> 00:07:28,800
It's like

155
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:30,310
knives were handed to him

156
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:32,720
when he sought to harm.

157
00:07:35,190 --> 00:07:36,240
Perhaps

158
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:37,600
heaven aided Zhang Song?

159
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:39,600
Heaven's aid or human design?

160
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,430
Xie Xi's hidden arrow
is extremely precious.

161
00:07:46,630 --> 00:07:48,120
He'd guard it carefully

162
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,630
and never misplace it.

163
00:07:50,190 --> 00:07:51,070
Yet it was lost

164
00:07:51,270 --> 00:07:52,390
and found by someone.

165
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:55,270
Regarding the plaque,
I inquired with Madam Lin.

166
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:57,070
The repair request was filed long ago,

167
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,600
but no one came.

168
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:01,040
Someone must deliberately delayed it.

169
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:03,270
You were close to Xie Xi

170
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:04,600
and had access

171
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:06,310
to his personal items.

172
00:08:07,530 --> 00:08:09,390
You transcribed the repair records,
didn't you?

173
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:15,510
What are you implying?

174
00:08:15,830 --> 00:08:17,360
You gave Zhang Song the arrow

175
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:20,070
and leaked the plaque's condition.

176
00:08:20,290 --> 00:08:22,120
You orchestrated everything.

177
00:08:22,830 --> 00:08:23,720
Lu Mingshu!

178
00:08:24,830 --> 00:08:26,830
I've no time for your nonsense.

179
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:28,390
I haven't finished yet.

180
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,310
Xie Xi treated you coldly.

181
00:08:30,310 --> 00:08:31,630
Lu Wencai threatened you.

182
00:08:31,950 --> 00:08:32,840
So you used

183
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:34,320
Zhang Song's vengeance

184
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,480
to kill two birds with one stone.

185
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,320
Your reasoning

186
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:43,200
seems logical

187
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:46,240
but remains mere conjecture.

188
00:08:47,630 --> 00:08:48,910
You have no proof.

189
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,550
Heaven

190
00:08:50,870 --> 00:08:51,840
witnesses all.

191
00:08:52,790 --> 00:08:53,910
You know the truth

192
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,720
in your heart.

193
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,000
Mingshu,

194
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,790
you wrong me.

195
00:09:06,270 --> 00:09:07,910
How could I act like this?

196
00:09:09,390 --> 00:09:10,230
However,

197
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,870
I wonder,

198
00:09:14,270 --> 00:09:15,840
if your family was destroyed

199
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,080
by villains,

200
00:09:18,030 --> 00:09:20,270
would you care about revenge methods?

201
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,270
What do you mean?

202
00:09:23,910 --> 00:09:24,840
Do you know...?

203
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:25,680
Su Tangli!

204
00:09:33,510 --> 00:09:34,390
You go out first.

205
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,160
I'll speak with her

206
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:37,720
privately.

207
00:09:53,910 --> 00:09:54,750
Mr. Lu,

208
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,320
Ying Xun said

209
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,720
you pleaded with Prince Rui

210
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:59,600
to spare me.

211
00:10:00,790 --> 00:10:01,630
Thank you.

212
00:10:01,910 --> 00:10:03,030
I promised to help you

213
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:05,870
escape the Imperial Music Office.

214
00:10:07,670 --> 00:10:09,000
I kept my word.

215
00:10:11,910 --> 00:10:13,360
But what about your promise to me?

216
00:10:14,790 --> 00:10:16,120
I'm sorry, Mr. Lu.

217
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:19,390
Earlier, Mingshu accused me
of manipulating others.

218
00:10:19,670 --> 00:10:21,270
I spoke rashly

219
00:10:21,270 --> 00:10:23,000
from anguish.

220
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,200
Please don't blame me.

221
00:10:25,510 --> 00:10:26,790
You're always composed.

222
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:30,320
Why lose composure

223
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:32,120
over mere words today?

224
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,720
After what I've endured,

225
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:39,840
I'm no longer

226
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:40,750
the Su Tangli

227
00:10:42,270 --> 00:10:44,790
who existed beyond worldly affairs.

228
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,160
Tangli,

229
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:54,600
I know you seek
to clear the mentor's name.

230
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:58,510
But justice differs from vengeance.

231
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:02,720
If you stray from righteousness,

232
00:11:04,270 --> 00:11:05,720
my mentor's spirit

233
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:06,790
won't rest.

234
00:11:11,630 --> 00:11:12,510
Mr. Lu,

235
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:16,240
do you doubt me?

236
00:11:20,630 --> 00:11:22,000
Belief matters less

237
00:11:23,510 --> 00:11:24,510
than your own awareness

238
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:27,360
of actions.

239
00:11:38,420 --> 00:11:42,100
(Education Without Bias)

240
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:07,080
Buddy,

241
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:09,030
are you still worried about Lady Su?

242
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,790
If your suspicions hold,

243
00:12:12,510 --> 00:12:14,390
though her hands are clean,

244
00:12:15,910 --> 00:12:16,790
her heart

245
00:12:16,790 --> 00:12:18,320
must be stained.

246
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,120
She asked me

247
00:12:20,870 --> 00:12:22,440
if my family was destroyed

248
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:23,510
by villains,

249
00:12:24,390 --> 00:12:26,510
would I care about revenge methods.

250
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:28,510
I don't know why,

251
00:12:28,510 --> 00:12:30,480
but this question haunts me.

252
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,320
So what do you think?

253
00:12:39,030 --> 00:12:40,320
I'd never spare the culprit.

254
00:12:46,650 --> 00:12:48,390
But I refuse to dwell
on such hypotheticals.

255
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,080
After all,

256
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:52,390
my loved ones are here with me.

257
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:55,440
Buddy,

258
00:12:56,390 --> 00:12:57,480
you and Mother

259
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:58,480
must stay well

260
00:12:59,510 --> 00:13:00,350
and be with me

261
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:02,030
forever.

262
00:13:05,870 --> 00:13:06,710
Okay.

263
00:13:21,870 --> 00:13:22,710
Your Majesty,

264
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:24,690
according to testimony
from Liu Xiankun's daughter

265
00:13:24,700 --> 00:13:26,000
regarding Su Changhua's case,

266
00:13:26,510 --> 00:13:27,720
Liu Xiankun was coerced

267
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:28,670
into falsely accusing Su

268
00:13:28,910 --> 00:13:29,910
of corruption.

269
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:30,960
I boldly

270
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,650
request Your Majesty
to reopen this case.

271
00:13:43,510 --> 00:13:45,080
I second it.

272
00:13:46,340 --> 00:13:48,140
(Emperor Da'an)

273
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:51,200
Your Majesty,

274
00:13:51,790 --> 00:13:53,720
the Su Changhua case
was thoroughly adjudicated.

275
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:55,150
Reopening it

276
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,720
may invite controversy

277
00:13:56,870 --> 00:13:58,630
and undermine the imperial authority.

278
00:13:59,670 --> 00:14:01,270
Mr. Yang, it's not true.

279
00:14:01,270 --> 00:14:03,630
Doubtful cases demand reinvestigation.

280
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:04,790
Turning a blind eye

281
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:07,630
will damage credibility.

282
00:14:13,750 --> 00:14:14,590
Your Majesty,

283
00:14:15,500 --> 00:14:17,630
three judicial ministries
have jointly tried Su's case

284
00:14:17,910 --> 00:14:19,670
after an exhaustive review.

285
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:21,510
Does Prince Rui

286
00:14:21,630 --> 00:14:22,630
imply

287
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:24,080
all three erred?

288
00:14:24,790 --> 00:14:26,240
If we reopen cases,

289
00:14:26,510 --> 00:14:28,120
should former judges

290
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:30,030
recuse themselves?

291
00:14:30,870 --> 00:14:32,910
I dare ask Prince Rui,

292
00:14:33,320 --> 00:14:35,320
is this merely a pretext

293
00:14:35,630 --> 00:14:37,080
to install your own candidates?

294
00:14:37,630 --> 00:14:39,670
I'm afraid that's what you really want.

295
00:14:42,910 --> 00:14:43,840
Mr. Han,

296
