596
00:26:58,070 --> 00:26:58,910
Forgot?

597
00:27:01,350 --> 00:27:02,190
Qingzhao,

598
00:27:02,750 --> 00:27:03,590
is that you?

599
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:17,760
This...

600
00:27:19,240 --> 00:27:20,550
She's utterly drunk.

601
00:27:21,030 --> 00:27:21,870
Mother,

602
00:27:22,100 --> 00:27:23,480
prepare some hangover soup for her.

603
00:27:23,960 --> 00:27:25,430
Get her inside.

604
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:29,920
Another cup.

605
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:32,070
It's all in the drink.

606
00:28:22,460 --> 00:28:23,980
(Wei Zhuo)

607
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:25,240
I mean no harm.

608
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:26,720
Madam, don't be afraid.

609
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:29,030
As a martial artist,

610
00:28:29,200 --> 00:28:30,160
I reacted instinctively

611
00:28:30,160 --> 00:28:31,200
to your move.

612
00:28:31,200 --> 00:28:33,000
My apologies.

613
00:28:36,110 --> 00:28:37,550
I mistook you

614
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:39,110
for a stalker earlier.

615
00:28:40,160 --> 00:28:41,270
And I overreacted.

616
00:28:41,790 --> 00:28:42,880
Please forgive my rudeness.

617
00:28:45,070 --> 00:28:46,790
My military training

618
00:28:46,960 --> 00:28:48,070
makes me overreact.

619
00:28:48,070 --> 00:28:48,910
Madam,

620
00:28:49,400 --> 00:28:50,270
are you unharmed?

621
00:28:52,070 --> 00:28:52,960
I'm fine.

622
00:28:55,640 --> 00:28:56,480
Who's there?

623
00:29:03,480 --> 00:29:04,320
It's settled.

624
00:29:08,750 --> 00:29:09,830
Thanks for your aid.

625
00:29:10,310 --> 00:29:11,750
I'm Zeng, thank you very much.

626
00:29:59,960 --> 00:30:00,800
Are you awake?

627
00:30:01,880 --> 00:30:03,160
Caught you,

628
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:04,510
Mr. Green Robe.

629
00:30:09,070 --> 00:30:10,440
Look closely now,

630
00:30:11,270 --> 00:30:12,350
who am I

631
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:13,480
on earth?

632
00:30:29,000 --> 00:30:29,880
No...

633
00:30:30,590 --> 00:30:32,510
You're not Song Qingzhao.

634
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:37,750
But you're like Buddy.

635
00:30:40,510 --> 00:30:42,350
I was never Song Qingzhao.

636
00:30:43,070 --> 00:30:44,200
I'm Lu Chang.

637
00:30:44,790 --> 00:30:46,030
Lu Chang?

638
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:48,980
Lu...

639
00:30:50,310 --> 00:30:52,550
Lu Chang is Buddy.

640
00:30:53,200 --> 00:30:54,590
No!

641
00:30:54,920 --> 00:30:55,760
Buddy...

642
00:30:55,960 --> 00:30:57,350
Buddy can't.

643
00:30:57,480 --> 00:30:58,320
No...

644
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:05,760
I know.

645
00:31:08,680 --> 00:31:10,270
Those memories

646
00:31:11,790 --> 00:31:12,630
are painful for you.

647
00:31:14,640 --> 00:31:15,550
Sometimes I wish

648
00:31:15,550 --> 00:31:17,160
you would never recall them.

649
00:31:18,440 --> 00:31:19,400
But sometimes...

650
00:31:30,200 --> 00:31:31,510
I was being selfish.

651
00:31:56,960 --> 00:31:57,960
Any findings?

652
00:31:58,240 --> 00:31:59,280
According to my investigation,

653
00:31:59,720 --> 00:32:00,920
Zeng never remarried.

654
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:02,550
She previously resided in Jianglin.

655
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:04,440
Recently, she moved to the capital.

656
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:05,910
The household only has Zeng,

657
00:32:06,030 --> 00:32:07,480
Lu Chang, and Lu Mingshu.

658
00:32:11,270 --> 00:32:13,400
It does appear to be Yuqing.

659
00:32:13,400 --> 00:32:14,850
(Zhang Shicheng)
It's all my fault.

660
00:32:14,880 --> 00:32:15,740
I assumed

661
00:32:15,740 --> 00:32:18,350
they perished in that year's flood.

662
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:21,160
Hence for all these years,

663
00:32:21,480 --> 00:32:23,270
our family remained separated.

664
00:32:23,880 --> 00:32:24,830
During my investigation,

665
00:32:25,310 --> 00:32:26,270
a man noticed me.

666
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,240
What man?

667
00:32:28,790 --> 00:32:29,630
I don't know.

668
00:32:30,550 --> 00:32:31,390
All right.

669
00:32:32,070 --> 00:32:32,910
Continue your search.

670
00:32:33,310 --> 00:32:34,150
Yes, Master.

671
00:32:39,270 --> 00:32:41,480
Congratulations on reuniting

672
00:32:41,640 --> 00:32:42,680
with your family.

673
00:32:46,110 --> 00:32:47,720
What celebration?

674
00:32:48,750 --> 00:32:49,590
Frankly,

675
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:50,920
it's all my fault back then.

676
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:52,510
I was obsessed with official duties.

677
00:32:52,960 --> 00:32:54,480
When they suffered,

678
00:32:55,480 --> 00:32:57,680
I failed to return promptly.

679
00:32:58,160 --> 00:32:59,000
Thus,

680
00:32:59,680 --> 00:33:02,270
we've been separated for over a decade.

681
00:33:02,550 --> 00:33:03,440
All these years,

682
00:33:04,350 --> 00:33:06,270
she has raised two children alone.

683
00:33:07,440 --> 00:33:09,750
She must have endured

684
00:33:10,640 --> 00:33:12,030
countless hardships.

685
00:33:13,480 --> 00:33:14,320
Master,

686
00:33:14,480 --> 00:33:16,480
bring them home

687
00:33:16,720 --> 00:33:18,270
and compensate them properly.

688
00:33:20,000 --> 00:33:22,030
I know Yuqing's temperament.

689
00:33:22,880 --> 00:33:24,310
She's strong-willed.

690
00:33:24,440 --> 00:33:26,350
Forgiveness won't come easily.

691
00:33:26,750 --> 00:33:28,350
Though you erred,

692
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:30,270
it was understandable.

693
00:33:31,070 --> 00:33:32,270
With sincere efforts

694
00:33:32,270 --> 00:33:34,590
over time,

695
00:33:34,920 --> 00:33:35,830
Madam Zeng

696
00:33:35,830 --> 00:33:37,070
is reasonable.

697
00:33:37,270 --> 00:33:39,110
She'll surely accept you

698
00:33:39,240 --> 00:33:40,070
and have a family reunion

699
00:33:40,510 --> 00:33:42,400
with you.

700
00:33:42,680 --> 00:33:43,680
May everything

701
00:33:44,720 --> 00:33:45,880
go smoothly.

702
00:33:47,070 --> 00:33:47,910
It will.

703
00:33:52,420 --> 00:33:55,100
(Old Madam Li)

704
00:34:06,750 --> 00:34:07,590
Auntie,

705
00:34:08,230 --> 00:34:09,630
are you physically well?

706
00:34:09,630 --> 00:34:10,920
Do you need to see a physician?

707
00:34:11,510 --> 00:34:12,350
Auntie,

708
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:14,880
I'm Wei Zhuo.

709
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:17,550
Your son's comrade.

710
00:34:17,550 --> 00:34:18,880
I'm here to visit you.

711
00:34:23,670 --> 00:34:24,670
Son!

712
00:34:26,360 --> 00:34:27,360
Son...

713
00:34:30,280 --> 00:34:32,070
You finally came

714
00:34:32,400 --> 00:34:35,190
to see me.

715
00:34:35,880 --> 00:34:36,880
Son,

716
00:34:36,880 --> 00:34:39,190
you married a good daughter-in-law.

717
00:34:40,400 --> 00:34:42,280
While you were away,

718
00:34:42,880 --> 00:34:44,590
she cared for me.

719
00:34:46,670 --> 00:34:48,280
She changed my clothes

720
00:34:48,480 --> 00:34:49,880
and cooked for me.

721
00:34:57,840 --> 00:34:58,840
(Something's wrong.)

722
00:34:59,280 --> 00:35:00,400
(Didn't Li's wife)

723
00:35:00,630 --> 00:35:02,000
(pass away long ago?)

724
00:35:03,880 --> 00:35:04,760
Son.

725
00:35:13,880 --> 00:35:14,720
Buddy,

726
00:35:19,320 --> 00:35:22,030
did you bring me home last night?

727
00:35:23,670 --> 00:35:25,320
I didn't embarrass myself, right?

728
00:35:28,550 --> 00:35:29,550
You don't remember?

729
00:35:33,070 --> 00:35:35,760
I drank a little...

730
00:35:37,070 --> 00:35:38,360
I swear never again.

731
00:35:44,230 --> 00:35:45,070
Buddy,

732
00:35:47,440 --> 00:35:48,500
it's better if you don't recall.

733
00:35:55,140 --> 00:36:02,140
(Prefectural Prince Residence)

734
00:36:09,000 --> 00:36:09,840
On your knees!

735
00:36:13,260 --> 00:36:14,480
(Prefectural Prince Residence)

736
00:36:14,480 --> 00:36:15,480
What's this?

737
00:36:15,480 --> 00:36:17,280
Prefectural Prince, County Princess,

738
00:36:18,110 --> 00:36:19,760
I failed

739
00:36:20,110 --> 00:36:21,230
in disciplining my son,

740
00:36:21,420 --> 00:36:23,190
allowing this wretch
to commit such offenses.

741
00:36:23,480 --> 00:36:24,320
Today,

742
00:36:25,100 --> 00:36:27,420
(Marquis Yongqing)
I bring him before this public gathering

743
00:36:27,920 --> 00:36:29,110
to atone for his crimes.

744
00:36:29,220 --> 00:36:31,190
(Prefectural Prince Residence)
We implore you to show mercy.

745
00:36:31,410 --> 00:36:33,030
Please forgive
this unworthy son of mine.

746
00:36:42,510 --> 00:36:43,350
Endure it.

747
00:36:47,120 --> 00:36:48,440
He's really striking him.

748
00:36:49,030 --> 00:36:49,870
Father!

749
00:36:50,700 --> 00:36:52,120
- Father!
- Will you remember this lesson?

750
00:36:53,000 --> 00:36:54,320
Do you understand your wrongs?

751
00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:56,110
Will you dare again?

752
00:36:59,100 --> 00:37:00,940
(Prefectural Prince Residence)

753
00:37:03,460 --> 00:37:04,470
I'll teach you.

754
00:37:09,480 --> 00:37:10,320
Uncle!

755
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:12,070
Uncle, stop beating him.

756
00:37:12,670 --> 00:37:13,510
Mr. Xie can't

757
00:37:14,670 --> 00:37:15,800
endure this.

758
00:37:16,400 --> 00:37:17,840
Apologize to County Princess at once!

759
00:37:18,320 --> 00:37:19,910
Yes, it's my fault.

760
00:37:20,070 --> 00:37:20,920
I apologize to you.

761
00:37:21,360 --> 00:37:22,590
But I was completely blinded

762
00:37:22,590 --> 00:37:23,480
by that criminal slave.

763
00:37:23,630 --> 00:37:25,150
I've always had you in my heart!

764
00:37:26,150 --> 00:37:26,990
Mr. Xie,

765
00:37:28,840 --> 00:37:30,440
I know you have me in mind.

766
00:37:30,960 --> 00:37:33,400
However, you were willing

767
00:37:33,840 --> 00:37:35,150
to violate laws for that Lady Su.

768
00:37:35,760 --> 00:37:36,600
Presumably,

769
00:37:36,960 --> 00:37:39,230
she takes precedence over me.

770
00:37:40,400 --> 00:37:41,240
Mr. Xie,

771
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:43,550
I don't wish to cause you distress.

772
00:37:44,100 --> 00:37:45,620
I'm willing to terminate our engagement

773
00:37:45,920 --> 00:37:48,280
to fulfill you and Lady Su.

774
00:37:49,860 --> 00:37:51,230
(Prefectural Prince Residence)

775
00:37:51,230 --> 00:37:52,800
Wen'an!

776
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:53,840
Let me explain.

777
00:37:53,840 --> 00:37:54,880
Please let me explain!

778
00:37:55,100 --> 00:37:56,280
County Princess is frightened.

779
00:37:56,400 --> 00:37:57,510
Don't let him startle her!

780
00:37:57,880 --> 00:37:59,440
Wen'an, please listen to me.

781
00:37:59,630 --> 00:38:00,710
Listen to my explanation!

782
00:38:03,400 --> 00:38:05,360
Lecher! Faithless scoundrel!

783
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:06,880
County Princess Wen'an is so good,

784
00:38:07,300 --> 00:38:08,510
yet you dare philander outside!

785
00:38:08,510 --> 00:38:09,590
Truly heartless!

786
00:38:09,710 --> 00:38:11,590
- My fault. I wronged you.
- Betrayer!

787
00:38:11,590 --> 00:38:12,550
I'm not like him.

788
00:38:12,550 --> 00:38:13,710
I didn't mean it.

789
00:38:14,880 --> 00:38:15,960
- Wen'an...
- Enough!

790
00:38:15,970 --> 00:38:17,440
Enough of this disgrace!

791
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:18,710
Beat this traitor to death!

792
00:38:18,710 --> 00:38:19,550
Strike him dead!

793
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:21,600
Wen'an...

794
00:38:27,700 --> 00:38:29,540
(Daqing Hall)

795
00:38:29,550 --> 00:38:30,390
Your Majesty,

796
00:38:30,600 --> 00:38:32,400
my foolish son
was kindhearted and nostalgic.

797
00:38:32,800 --> 00:38:34,320
He was beguiled by that criminal slave.

798
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:35,800
His momentary negligence

799
00:38:35,920 --> 00:38:37,030
caused grave errors.

800
00:38:38,000 --> 00:38:39,070
I beseech Your Majesty,

801
00:38:39,230 --> 00:38:41,360
considering my years of loyalty,

802
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:42,640
to show leniency

803
00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:44,000
and pardon my son.

804
00:38:49,030 --> 00:38:49,870
Your Majesty,

805
00:38:50,320 --> 00:38:51,880
this can't be lightly forgiven.

806
00:38:52,630 --> 00:38:53,480
Xie Xi's illicit relations

807
00:38:53,630 --> 00:38:54,840
with criminal slaves

808
00:38:55,440 --> 00:38:57,800
and abuse of Marquis Yongqing's authority
to forge documents

809
00:38:58,440 --> 00:39:00,960
are illegal and morally corrupt.

810
00:39:01,840 --> 00:39:03,110
My daughter's years

811
00:39:03,440 --> 00:39:05,360
of devotion

812
00:39:06,150 --> 00:39:07,190
only met with deception

813
00:39:07,760 --> 00:39:09,030
and infidelity!

814
00:39:12,670 --> 00:39:14,440
Marquis Yongqing failed parental duties

815
00:39:14,920 --> 00:39:16,000
and abused power!

816
00:39:16,510 --> 00:39:19,150
I implore Your Majesty
to annul the engagement

817
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:20,200
and severely punish

818
00:39:20,510 --> 00:39:22,400
the entire Marquis household!

819
00:39:33,480 --> 00:39:34,320
Your Majesty,

820
00:39:34,480 --> 00:39:35,320
Marquis Yongqing

821
00:39:35,320 --> 00:39:36,710
remains an important court pillar.

822
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:39,400
Moreover,
Prince Rui learned martial arts

823
00:39:39,710 --> 00:39:40,840
from him since childhood.

824
00:39:41,280 --> 00:39:42,150
I hope Your Majesty

825
00:39:42,400 --> 00:39:43,800
will show mercy,

826
00:39:44,150 --> 00:39:45,110
considering

827
00:39:45,230 --> 00:39:46,280
his past connections.

828
00:39:55,000 --> 00:39:55,840
Prince Rui,

829
00:39:56,760 --> 00:39:58,840
Marquis Yongqing was

830
00:39:58,840 --> 00:40:00,230
indeed your tutor.

831
00:40:00,800 --> 00:40:02,920
What's your view on this matter?

832
00:40:09,760 --> 00:40:10,600
Your Majesty,

833
00:40:11,840 --> 00:40:12,680
those who betray

834
00:40:13,630 --> 00:40:14,480
the imperial grace

835
00:40:15,150 --> 00:40:16,070
and disrupt court order

836
00:40:16,190 --> 00:40:17,190
must be punished by law

837
00:40:17,740 --> 00:40:18,760
to satisfy public justice.

838
00:40:22,320 --> 00:40:23,760
I second it.

839
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:27,030
I second it!

840
00:40:32,530 --> 00:40:34,280
Henceforth, Xie Xi,
son of Marquis Yongqing,

841
00:40:34,400 --> 00:40:37,550
is stripped of engagement
to County Princess Wen'an,

842
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:38,880
demoted to commoner status,

843
00:40:39,510 --> 00:40:41,960
and permanently barred
from imperial examinations.

844
00:40:42,190 --> 00:40:43,800
Marquis Yongqing is removed

845
00:40:43,800 --> 00:40:44,920
as Minister of War

846
00:40:45,150 --> 00:40:47,000
for negligence and poor parenting,

847
00:40:47,510 --> 00:40:49,030
but retains his title

848
00:40:49,360 --> 00:40:50,710
in recognition of past merits.

849
00:40:56,300 --> 00:40:59,820
(Daqing Hall)

850
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:01,280
Using a wastrel

851
00:41:01,510 --> 00:41:02,480
to deprive Prince Rui

852
00:41:02,590 --> 00:41:04,480
of Marquis Yongqing's support.

853
00:41:05,440 --> 00:41:07,110
What an effortless strategy!

854
00:41:09,630 --> 00:41:10,710
You show brilliant insight.

855
00:41:12,760 --> 00:41:13,600
Yet Prince Rui,

856
00:41:14,360 --> 00:41:15,920
despite the heavy losses,

857
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:18,110
didn't plead for mercy.

858
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:20,920
It surprised me somewhat.

859
00:41:21,710 --> 00:41:22,550
So what?

860
00:41:23,110 --> 00:41:24,590
Prince Rui followed legal procedures.

861
00:41:24,590 --> 00:41:26,320
Though avoiding censure
from the officials,

862
00:41:26,630 --> 00:41:28,440
his abandonment of the Xie Family

863
00:41:28,440 --> 00:41:29,800
reveals his cold-hearted nature

864
00:41:29,800 --> 00:41:31,630
to others.

865
00:41:32,110 --> 00:41:32,950
As a result,

866
00:41:33,320 --> 00:41:34,320
those court observers

867
00:41:34,320 --> 00:41:35,360
will surely

868
00:41:35,710 --> 00:41:37,280
align with Your Highness.

869
00:41:48,700 --> 00:41:51,500
(New Dawn)

870
00:42:04,760 --> 00:42:06,110
How does it feel to be reduced

871
00:42:06,590 --> 00:42:08,920
to a commoner and forever barred

872
00:42:09,920 --> 00:42:10,960
from examinations?

873
00:42:11,920 --> 00:42:14,360
Truly, never infuriate a woman.

874
00:42:14,590 --> 00:42:16,590
I saved your life,

875
00:42:16,710 --> 00:42:18,960
yet you brought me to this ruin.

876
00:42:19,110 --> 00:42:21,320
Where's your conscience?

877
00:42:23,510 --> 00:42:24,400
Conscience?

878
00:42:25,110 --> 00:42:26,670
When you tried to kill me

879
00:42:27,360 --> 00:42:28,880
near the cliff

880
00:42:29,320 --> 00:42:30,920
to secure your position,

881
00:42:30,920 --> 00:42:32,320
where was your conscience?

882
00:42:32,630 --> 00:42:34,510
When you sacrificed me in court

883
00:42:34,880 --> 00:42:36,400
to save yourself,

884
00:42:36,400 --> 00:42:38,000
where was your conscience?

885
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:40,400
All your promises of protection,

886
00:42:40,920 --> 00:42:41,760
love,

887
00:42:42,050 --> 00:42:43,190
and reversing the case for me

888
00:42:44,760 --> 00:42:46,840
were lies to bask

889
00:42:46,840 --> 00:42:48,670
